'group_vars'is a standard Ansible directory used to store variable files that
 apply to groups of hosts defined in your Ansible inventory (inventory. ini).

    Create encrypted .env (safe for repo)
        ansible-vault create group_vars/common_secrets.yml

    Transform unencrypted yaml into encrypted secret
        ansible-vault encrypt group_vars/unencrypted_secrets.yml

    Edit existing file
        ansible-vault edit secret.yml

    View encrypted file
        ansible-vault view secret.yml